-- Chavez Medical Team Continuing Surgery in Cuba, Villegas Says
-- B y   J o s e   O r o z c o
-- 2012-12-11T22:11:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-11/chavez-medical-team-continuing-surgery-in-cuba-villegas-says.html
A team of doctors in Cuba is
continuing to operate on Venezuelan President  Hugo Chavez ,
information minister Ernesto Villegas said today in a national
address.  “The surgery scheduled for today is continuing as
planned,” Villegas said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
